<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>10: it’s only 1 group of 10.</li>
      <li>20: I added 10 more on to the first answer.</li>
      <li>30: I added <m>10+10+10</m>.</li>
      <li>40: I counted by 10.  </li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


